        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-8 ">
          <h1 class="center spinz-blue">About Us</h1>
          <p>
          SpinzCity was created by people who love tennis just like you do! We created this fun platform to help you improve your tennis, have a little fun, and become a better overall person! SpinzCity is a simple, fun, and free way to be active with tennis! </p>
          <p>
          The program is designed to work in concert with or independent of private or group tennis instruction. The goal of the program is to develop eye-hand coordination skills appropriate for the age of your tennis player. In addition, students will have an opportunity to learn about tennis through important off-court skills included in this program.
          </p>
          <p>
          Too often with tennis, children are exposed to the sport through weekly lessons and find progress difficult. Other programs nurture the need for practice but do not help create knowledgeable “tennis citizens” who become fans of the sport.
          </p>
          <p>
          This program hopes to capitalize on the natural curiosity of your tennis player and the excitement of achieving goals. With your support, you will see your tennis player not only gaining skills but a greater interest in the sport of tennis. Together, we can give your tennis player the best possible change to become a lifetime tennis player and supporter!
          </p>
        </div>
        
